result.title: CSX Corp. Announces Third Quarter 2025 Results
result.text: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Oct. 16, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- CSX Corp. (NASDAQ: CSX) today announced third quarter operating income of $1.09 billion and net earnings of $694 million, or $0.37 per share. Excluding a non-cash goodwill impairment of $164 million in this year's third quarter results, adjusted operating income was $1.25 billion and adjusted net earnings were $818 million, or $0.44 per share. In the third quarter of 2024, the company reported operating income of $1.35 billion and net earnings of $894 million, or $0.46 per share.
